01:19:03,687 --> 01:19:06,622
Shared responsibility and shared sacrifice.

1197
01:19:06,757 --> 01:19:10,818
<i>For those of you who are fortunate enough
to earn more than $200,000 a year,</i>

1198
01:19:10,961 --> 01:19:13,555
