01:19:47,898 --> 01:19:49,422
to a Wall Street equity firm.

1213
01:19:49,566 --> 01:19:52,807
I believe the residents of Bolton Village
would have much preferred a tax increase

1214
01:19:52,937 --> 01:19:54,962
to an eviction notice.

1215
01:19:55,105 --> 01:19:57,596
- I'm telling you this, Councilman:
no matter where a New Yorker lives,

1216
01:19:57,741 --> 01:20:00,642
<i>nobody wants a tax increase.</i>

1217
01:20:00,778 --> 01:20:02,109
