1228
01:20:36,080 --> 01:20:39,846
<i>Solstein Donagan did not buy Bolton Village
to get into the landlord business.</i>

1229
01:20:39,984 --> 01:20:43,545
<i>Solstein Donagan bought Bolton Village
to get into the skyline business.</i>

1230
01:20:43,687 --> 01:20:45,985
