1234
01:20:55,199 --> 01:20:58,498
- I don't how much clearer
I can make it for you.

1235
01:20:58,635 --> 01:21:00,500
<i>To the people of Bolton Village,</i>

1236
01:21:00,637 --> 01:21:03,504
<i>there's only one reason I got into this deal.</i>

1237
01:21:03,640 --> 01:21:05,540
<i>Because I want better for you.</i>

1238
01:21:05,676 --> 01:21:07,075
There is a new day dawning

1239
01:21:07,211 --> 01:21:10,180
<i>in Bolton Village.
And if Solstein Donagan,</i>

1240
01:21:10,314 --> 01:21:14,080
if they step out of line,
if they don't fulfill their promises,

1241
01:21:14,218 --> 01:21:17,710
<i>then I will smack them back into shape.</i>

1242
01:21:17,855 --> 01:21:19,755
<i>That is my oath.</i>

1243
01:21:19,890 --> 01:21:21,881
- Well, unfortunately for you, Mayor,
we're all well aware

1244
01:21:22,026 --> 01:21:24,051
