1262
01:22:04,435 --> 01:22:06,096
The issue is dire.

1263
01:22:06,236 --> 01:22:08,932
Because you and your cronies
have rigged the game.

1264
01:22:09,073 --> 01:22:13,407
And honest, hardworking New Yorkers
recognize that nothing will change.

1265
01:22:13,544 --> 01:22:17,241
Nothing will ever change
if we continue to elect men like this.

1266
01:22:17,381 --> 01:22:19,508
- Tell me things have not changed!

1267
01:22:20,084 --> 01:22:22,211
When I was elected mayor,

1268
01:22:22,352 --> 01:22:24,946
