Broken.

1269
01:22:25,089 --> 01:22:27,956
Step by step, I've been getting it fixed.

1270
01:22:28,092 --> 01:22:31,584
Bolton Village
is just another one of those steps.

1271
01:22:31,728 --> 01:22:33,025
Tell me things haven't changed.

1272
01:22:33,163 --> 01:22:37,156
