and tell them that!

1276
01:22:44,975 --> 01:22:47,656
When you step out of your house,
in the morning, with your children,

1277
01:22:47,678 --> 01:22:50,408
you take 'em to the parks
of the five boroughs, d'you feel safe?

1278
01:22:50,547 --> 01:22:51,946
Yes, you do,

1279
01:22:52,082 --> 01:22:54,642
