1280
01:22:54,785 --> 01:22:57,310
That's us, working together,
getting it fixed.

1281
01:22:57,454 --> 01:22:59,251
Tell me things haven't changed.

1282
01:22:59,389 --> 01:23:01,619
- Yeah!
- That's right, Mayor!

1283
01:23:05,329 --> 01:23:08,958
- Councilman Valliant,
the original question still remains.

1284
01:23:09,099 --> 01:23:11,727
What would you have done
to reverse the debt?

1285
01:23:12,970 --> 01:23:14,904
- Tha...
- Don't worry about it, Councilman!

