01:24:32,683 --> 01:24:35,709
What are you saying?
Tell me what the fuck is going on!

1305
01:24:35,852 --> 01:24:37,251
- Please stop hitting me!

1306
01:24:37,387 --> 01:24:39,150
I didn't know!

1307
01:24:40,224 --> 01:24:42,419
I was just there to give him something!

1308
01:24:42,559 --> 01:24:45,460
I-I was down on the corner
and I was waiting for him,

1309
01:24:45,596 --> 01:24:47,427
and I saw him coming down the stairs

1310
01:24:47,564 --> 01:24:49,088
and I waved, okay?

1311
01:24:49,233 --> 01:24:52,669
I was gonna give him something
to help Valliant win!

1312
01:24:52,803 --> 01:24:55,636
To help Valliant bring down
that sonofabitch Hostetler!

1313
01:24:55,772 --> 01:24:58,570
- That doesn't make any sense, Todd.
Hostetler's your father's friend.

1314
01:24:58,709 --> 01:25:00,233
- Fuck my father!!

1315
01:25:01,612 --> 01:25:03,512
